Entries.Name: 28 Days Later
Entries.Title: 28 Days Later
Entries.Description: Hailed as the most frightening film since The Exorcist, acclaimed Director Danny Boyle's visionary take on zombie horror "isn't just scary...it's absolutely terrifying" (Access Hollywood).
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Forget walking dead, the zombies are fast as hell in Danny Boyle’s savage tale that helped resurrect a genre.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Forget walking dead, the zombies are fast as hell in Danny Boyle’s savage tale that helped resurrect a genre.

Entries.Name: 30 Minutes Or Less
Entries.Title: 30 Minutes Or Less
Entries.Description: In 30 Minutes or Less, a small town pizza delivery guy is kidnapped and forced to rob a bank in mere hours by two wanna-be criminal masterminds.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Eisenberg and Ansari are the bungling criminals of our dreams in a breakneck comedy from the director of Zombieland.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Eisenberg and Ansari are the bungling criminals of our dreams in a breakneck comedy from the director of Zombieland.

Entries.Name: 50 First Dates
Entries.Title: 50 First Dates
Entries.Description: A man falls in love with a woman who suffers from severe short-term memory loss.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: It's the Pennsylvania Polka for Adam Sandler as he's forced into a romantic loop of Groundhog Day proportions.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: It's the Pennsylvania Polka for Adam Sandler as he's forced into a romantic loop of Groundhog Day proportions.

Entries.Name: The 6th Day
Entries.Title: The 6th Day
Entries.Description: Human cloning technology has fallen into destructive  corrupt hands but one man refuses to be a pawn in the deadly conspiracy.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Two Schwarzeneggers are better than one as Arnold goes back to the future in a smart, action-filled return to form.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Two Schwarzeneggers are better than one as Arnold goes back to the future in a smart, action-filled return to form.

Entries.Name: Action Figures
Entries.Title: Action Figures
Entries.Description: Action Figures is the directorial debut of Travis Pastrana, Nitro Circus founder and 17-time X Game medalist.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Sometimes, you just have to drive a motocross bike off a 50-foot ramp, execute a triple flip, and land in a badass pile of dirt: The Movie.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Sometimes, you just have to drive a motocross bike off a 50-foot ramp, execute a triple flip, and land in a badass pile of dirt: The Movie.

Entries.Name: Action Figures 2
Entries.Title: Action Figures 2
Entries.Description: The much-anticipated sequel to Travis Pastrana’s hit action-sports movie, Action Figures. The Nitro Circus founder and X Games champ does it again with more gravity-flouting, sanity-shattering stunts.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: If you don’t think Travis Pastrana and his Nitro Circus friends are out of their helmeted gourds, you’re not paying attention.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: If you don’t think Travis Pastrana and his Nitro Circus friends are out of their helmeted gourds, you’re not paying attention.

Entries.Name: Age Of Kill
Entries.Title: Age Of Kill
Entries.Description: A black ops sniper is blackmailed by a psychotic international terrorist into killing 6 unrelated people in 6 hours... but there is more to the victims than meets the eye.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: If your daughter’s gonna get taken, being a badass black ops sniper is a plus.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: If your daughter’s gonna get taken, being a badass black ops sniper is a plus.

Entries.Name: Ali G Indahouse
Entries.Title: Ali G Indahouse
Entries.Description: Comedy sensation Sacha Baron Cohen (Borat) stars as Ali G, the white, gangsta-rapper wannabe who gets entangled in an evil Chancellor’s plot to overthrow Great Britain’s Prime Minister.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Sacha Baron Cohen's clueless rapper-wannabe reps hilarious cliches while knocking them down.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Sacha Baron Cohen's clueless rapper-wannabe reps hilarious cliches while knocking them down.

Entries.Name: An Officer And A Gentleman
Entries.Title: An Officer And A Gentleman
Entries.Description: A streetwise misfit struggles to realize his dream of becoming a Naval Aviation Officer.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Richard Gere and Debra Winger get swept away in love and war in a shamelessly romantic ’80s gem.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Richard Gere and Debra Winger get swept away in love and war in a shamelessly romantic ’80s gem.

Entries.Name: Angel Of Death
Entries.Title: Angel Of Death
Entries.Description: Comic book legend Ed Brubaker's tale of a stoic assassin whose life takes a turn after six inches of cold steel wind up in her cranium.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Stunt goddess Zoe Bell may be the go-to action double for Hollywood, but here her mad skills take top billing.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Stunt goddess Zoe Bell may be the go-to action double for Hollywood, but here her mad skills take top billing.

Entries.Name: Arena
Entries.Title: Arena
Entries.Description: One sadistically savvy businessman has created an empire with his brutal fight-to-the-death gladiator website. After being abducted and tortured, his newest gladiator must fight for his life.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: It's the gorier and more savage version of The Hunger Games with a twist and a kick of Samuel L. Jackson.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: It's the gorier and more savage version of The Hunger Games with a twist and a kick of Samuel L. Jackson.

Entries.Name: The Art Of War
Entries.Title: The Art Of War
Entries.Description: Wesley Snipes (The Player) stars in this explosive thriller as a secret agent wrongly accused of assassinating world leaders.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Snipes demos the art of ass-kicking in an adrenaline rush that hits bullseye after bullseye.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Snipes demos the art of ass-kicking in an adrenaline rush that hits bullseye after bullseye.

Entries.Name: Avengers Confidential: Black Widow & Punisher
Entries.Title: Avengers Confidential: Black Widow & Punisher
Entries.Description: Detained by the clandestine law enforcement organization, Nick Fury offers the Punisher his freedom in exchange for one mission; work with Black Widow and stop the terrorist group known as LEVIATHAN.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Fanboys take note: Marvel's Avengers are saving the world again in stunning animation and epic fight scenes.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Fanboys take note: Marvel's Avengers are saving the world again in stunning animation and epic fight scenes.

Entries.Name: Backwash
Entries.Title: Backwash
Entries.Description: After a slacker inadvertently robs a bank armed only with a large salami, he and his friends must deal with the fallout of their sudden wealth.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: A roster of A-list celebs narrate this superbly imaginative roadtrip comedy from the director of Harold & Kumar.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: A roster of A-list celebs narrate this superbly imaginative roadtrip comedy from the director of Harold & Kumar.

Entries.Name: The Bannen Way
Entries.Title: The Bannen Way
Entries.Description: He’s a playboy con man who's one step away from going straight. But when his last score goes bad he has a choice: the cops, the mob or the Bannen Way.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Academy Award-nominated actors provide supporting roles to a break-out newbie in this slick con-man story.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Academy Award-nominated actors provide supporting roles to a break-out newbie in this slick con-man story.

Entries.Name: Batman: The Killing Joke
Entries.Title: Batman: The Killing Joke
Entries.Description: Joker wages a psychological war on Batman and leaves scars on the Dark Knight that even time won't heal.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Mark Hammil voices the most twisted villain in superhero history and everyone loses their minds.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Mark Hammil voices the most twisted villain in superhero history and everyone loses their minds.

Entries.Name: Black Jack: The Movie
Entries.Title: Black Jack: The Movie
Entries.Description: The adventures of the unlicensed but genius doctor Black Jack, who encounters extraordinary people and phenomena as he attends to unusual medical cases.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: This R-rated medical mystery wastes no time drawing you in and grossing you out.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: This R-rated medical mystery wastes no time drawing you in and grossing you out.

Entries.Name: Blood: The Last Vampire
Entries.Title: Blood: The Last Vampire
Entries.Description: Yakota Air Force Base, it's up to Saya, a grim woman of mysterious origin, and her magic sword to rid the base, and the planet, of these unwelcome and menacing monsters.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: The live-action adaptation of Blood+ delivers on killer samurai battles and demon fights.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: The live-action adaptation of Blood+ delivers on killer samurai battles and demon fights.

Entries.Name: Bram Stoker’s Dracula
Entries.Title: Bram Stoker’s Dracula
Entries.Description: Based on Bram Stoker's classic and dark love story about the vampire who travels from Eastern Europe to England in search of human love.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: An Oscar award-winning horror flick helmed by Francis Ford Coppola  so visceral you can practically taste the blood.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: An Oscar award-winning horror flick helmed by Francis Ford Coppola  so visceral you can practically taste the blood.

Entries.Name: Bucky Larson: Born To Be A Star
Entries.Title: Bucky Larson: Born To Be A Star
Entries.Description: A kid from the Midwest moves out to Hollywood in order to follow in his parents footsteps -- and become a porn star.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Critics may turn up their noses  but Nick Swardson's total commitment to rabbit-toothed idiocy wins us over.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Critics may turn up their noses  but Nick Swardson's total commitment to rabbit-toothed idiocy wins us over.
